<h2> How do I Mark Down Plugin to RubyMine? </h2>
<ul style="list-style: none;">
  <li><p> RubyMine/Preferences/Plugins</p></li>
  <li><p> Click the Browse Repositories button</p></li>
  <li><p> Search for markdown</p></li>
  <li><p> Install the Markdown plugin</p></li>
  <li><p> Restart RubyMine when prompted</p></li>
  <li><p> Now when you edit Markdown documents, you can see the formatted version</p></li>
</ul>
